      "description": "Priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward, budget-friendly transportation with plenty of usable life for the right buyer. It shows age and wear consistent with an older pre-owned vehicle, but it remains a practical option for commuting, errands, or as an inexpensive backup. A great opportunity to own at a low entry price from a seller committed to clear, honest representation.",
