    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels without spending a fortune? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option with plenty of usable life left for the right buyer. Great for a cheap runabout, first project, or someone who doesn\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC. If you want something straightforward, approachable, and priced to sell, this could be a great fit.",
