    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough-running driver/project with a strong mechanical feel and plenty of usable life for the next owner. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission engages as it should, and it has the kind of straightforward, serviceable setup enthusiasts appreciate. Cosmetics and overall condition reflect age and use, so it\u2019s best suited for someone who wants an affordable commuter, shop truck, or solid platform to sort and improve over time. Priced to move while still reflecting its dependable core mechanicals.",
