    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of personality you notice right away\u2014the sort of honest, road-worn machine that still turns heads because it feels like it has stories left to tell. Perfect for someone who loves a hands-on project, needs an inexpensive set of wheels, or wants a platform with real character, it offers a chance to make it your own without a huge upfront cost. If you appreciate charm, grit, and possibility over showroom polish, this one is easy to root for.",
      "price": 5900.0,
