      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable and honest, this vehicle is a practical choice for a budget-conscious buyer seeking basic transportation or a solid project opportunity. It delivers straightforward value with an accessible entry price, making it well-suited for commuting, first-time ownership, or weekend DIY improvement. If you want inexpensive wheels with potential, this is a compelling option worth a look.",
