    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a handy runaround, or a project with potential. Priced fairly and represented honestly, it\u2019s the kind of car that makes sense if you want value without spending a fortune. If you appreciate a straightforward sale and a car that can still do a job, this one is well worth a look.",
